title: Travelling over the Malá Fatra region
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
In the final episode of this summer series, we will immerse ourselves in exploring Žilina, rafting the Váh river, and hiking some of the most beautiful peaks in Slovakia. 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
Guests: Ivan the rafter, David Cartwright, Róbert Hlaváč
